      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPECIAL PLAYERS (6) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.11) at this track behind Paw Brody in a Grade 4/5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ZIVA DIVA (1) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a half a length third (25.83) over 450m at Ballarat. Winning chance. DREAM BIG (3) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (22.84) at this track in a T3 RSTW over 400m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. One of the prime contenders. VOLTS (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
